body:
#### PR description:

This PR is a follow-up to https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/38195, introducing miscellaneous improvements to the `CondFormats/PCLConfig` package.
   * added integer and string parameter size `enum`s for not yet used parameters and changed the logic to calculate the payload version
   * fully templated also the `AlignPCLThresholdsWriter` writer class;
   * improved the `printAll()` method of `AlignPCLThresholdsHG` in order to give a more synoptic view of the parameters;
   * complemented unit tests in order to test both LG and HG classes;

#### PR validation:

run the dedicated unit tests: `scram b runtests`

